WEBVTT

00:02:59.840 --> 00:03:02.456
Katika tabaka la hali ya kati 
au kaya tajiri,

00:03:02.480 --> 00:03:04.256
kama mwanafunzi atakuwa na shida

00:03:04.280 --> 00:03:08.216
kuna uwezekano mkubwa kuwa 
mzazi au mwalimu atakuja kumsaidia

00:03:08.240 --> 00:03:10.010
hata asipoomba msaada.

00:03:10.010 --> 00:03:12.366
Lakini, kama mtoto huyo 
amekulia katika umaskini

00:03:12.366 --> 00:03:13.600
na hataomba msaada,

00:03:14.240 --> 00:03:16.560
kuna uwezekano mkubwa 
hakuna atakayemsaidia.

00:03:16.880 --> 00:03:19.880
Hakuna wigo wa usalama wa kijamii 
unaopatikana.

00:03:21.090 --> 00:03:22.536
Kwa hiyo miaka saba iliyopita,

00:03:22.560 --> 00:03:25.376
Nilianza kuboresha 
mfumo wetu wa elimu ya umma

00:03:25.400 --> 00:03:28.000
nikichukua taswira 
ya mtazamo wangu wa moja kwa moja.

00:03:28.960 --> 00:03:30.532
Na nilianza na shule ya kiangazi.